T.query: select e.emp_no  as emp_no ,salary,first_name,last_name,birth_date,hire_date,from_date  from employees e join salaries s on e.emp_no = s.emp_no where e.emp_no < 10500 or (s.from_date=s.to_date and s.from_date > '1990-01-01') or e.last_name like 'Alb%' or s.to_date < '1986-01-01' or e.birth_date > '1965-01-01' or s.salary > 150000;
